- **Nervous System Match** ("you're exactly my speed") — both know this is different, intense, necessary
- **Suppressed Parts Surfacing** — everything they've been suppressing their whole lives gets space here
- **Intensity as Safety Signal** — can't-separate feeling is how they recognize it's real
- **Saliva Boundary** (non-negotiable from first kiss) — honored without negotiation during intensity
- **Mutual Care Recognition** (coat buttoning during her overwhelm) — she's in sensory hell but still tracks him; proof of mutual attention
- **Reciprocity Over Performance** — foundational baseline in a bubble (not what acts, but mutual presence and feral response)
- **Breathing Space Required** — after bubble intensity, real life has to come back in; integration necessary

